flowchart TD
    enter["stopTask(taskId)"] --> s1{"task.status
!== 'running'?"}
    s1 -->|是| err1["throw StopTaskError
code: 'not_running'"]
    s1 -->|否| s2{"isLocalShellTask
(task)?"}
    s2 -->|是| bash_action["抑制 exit code 137 通知
（LocalShellTask 特有）
task 类型收窄为 LocalShellTaskState"]
    s2 -->|否| agent_action["跳过通知抑制
（Agent 任务有实际错误载荷）"]
    bash_action & agent_action --> s3["const command =
isLocalShellTask(task)
? task.command
: task.description"]
    s3 --> kill["发送 SIGKILL
更新 status = killed"]
